      <li><strong>No shared service rate limits</strong> &mdash; Make.com calls the Google Docs API via OAuth, separate from the shared Apps Script consumer pool.</li>
      <li><strong>No document create cap</strong> &mdash; the 250/day consumer limit applies to Apps Script internal calls only.</li>
    </ul>
