  </div>

  <h2 id="outgrown">When You Have Outgrown Apps Script Entirely</h2>
  <p>The clearest signal: the workflow behaves differently depending on the time of day. That&apos;s time-dependent behaviour caused by daily quota exhaustion. The fix structure is:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Trigger in Apps Script &mdash; lightweight event detection only</li>
    <li>Process in a dedicated execution layer &mdash; Make.com, a Cloud Function, or dedicated API</li>
    <li>Write results back only after the heavy work is complete</li>
  </ul>

