  <p><strong>Apps Script detects the event. Make.com does the processing. The result lands back in Sheets.</strong> This removes the quota ceiling from every expensive operation. The <a href="/blog/make-com-shopify-automation-guide">Make.com for Shopify complete guide</a> covers the full setup.</p>

